OL,3,CMan charged after fatal stabbing in
OL,4,Csouth London
OL,6,FA man has been charged with murder
OL,7,Ffollowing a fatal stabbing in south
OL,8,FLondon.
OL,10,FPolice were called at about 10.40am on
OL,11,FSunday after reports of a number of
OL,12,Fpeople stabbed in East Street,
OL,13,FWalworth.
OL,15,FThree people were found with injuries
OL,16,Fand Hilkiah McLeggan, 77, from
OL,17,FSouthwark, was pronounced dead at the
OL,18,Fscene, the Metropolitan Police said.
