OL,3,CMan charged after fatal stabbing in
OL,4,Csouth London
OL,6,FThe force confirmed his identity on
OL,7,FMonday and said his family is
OL,8,Freceiving support from specialist
OL,9,Fofficers.
OL,11,FMusse Ali, 66, of no fixed address,
OL,12,Fhas been charged with one count of
OL,13,Fmurder and two counts of attempted
OL,14,Fmurder, and is due to appear at
OL,15,FCroydon Magistrates' Court on Tuesday,
OL,16,Fthe Met said.
OL,18,FTwo other men were taken to hospital
OL,19,Fwith serious injuries. Both victims
OL,20,Fremain in hospital, one of them in a
OL,21,Fcritical condition.
