OL,4,Csouth London
OL,6,FChief Superintendent Seb Adjei-Addoh,
OL,7,Flead for policing in Southwark, warned
OL,8,Fsocial media posts are circulating
OL,9,Fthat incorrectly suggest it was a
OL,10,Fterrorist incident.
OL,12,FHe said: "This was a horrific incident
OL,13,Fwhere a man had lost his life and two
OL,14,Fother people received serious injuries.
OL,16,F"The incident has understandably
OL,17,Fcaused concern amongst the local
OL,18,Fcommunity.
