OL,6,F"There will be an increased policing
OL,7,Fpresence in the Walworth area as we
OL,8,Fwork alongside our partners to provide
OL,9,Freassurance to local people and small
OL,10,Fbusinesses operating in East Street.
OL,12,F"We are aware of posts circulating on
OL,13,Fsocial media, implying that this was a
OL,14,Fterrorist incident. Our inquiries
OL,15,Findicate this is not the case and we
OL,16,Fask the public not to speculate."
