OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Alison
OL,7,FFoxwell said: "Our officers have
OL,8,Fworked quickly to investigate this
OL,9,Ftragic incident and secure these
OL,10,Fcharges.
OL,12,F"I would like to thank the members of
OL,13,Fthe public who have assisted us so far
OL,14,Fand encourage anyone who hasn't spoken
OL,15,Fwith us to get in contact."
OL,17,FThe Metropolitan Police are asking for
OL,18,Fanyone with information to call 101,
OL,19,For message @MetCC on X quoting
OL,20,Freference 2690/10Nov.
